      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/occ-issues-enforcement-action-against-wells-fargo-2024-09-12/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[富国银行股价周四下跌，此前美国银行业监管机构发现该行针对洗钱和其他非法交易的保障措施过于松懈，限制了其在高风险业务领域的扩张能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/occ-issues-enforcement-action-against-wells-fargo-2024-09-12/</guid>
